     |---------|---------|--------|
     | **Toyota** | Japan | Leader in R&D; 2027 production target |
     | **Nissan** | Japan | All-solid-state development; 2028 target |
     | **Honda** | Japan | Demonstration line operating; production process launch March 2025 |
     | **Mercedes-Benz** | Germany | Road tests with Factorial Energy |
     | **BMW** | Germany | Testing with Solid Power |
     | **Volkswagen** | Germany | Backing QuantumScape |
     | **Stellantis** | Multiple | Factorial Energy partnership; Dodge Charger Daytona EVs |
     | **Rimac** | Croatia | Technology showcase at IAA 2025 |
     | **Hyundai** | South Korea | Patent filings; cost-reducing design |
     
     ### Battery Manufacturers & Startups
     
     | Company | Country | Key Partnerships | Focus |
